{"tid":844512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傘運紀錄片　入圍金馬獎","createTime":"2018-10-02T02:52:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T12:39:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2440bf5be666200c07a8ac2c88c1c1b45e603835","tid":844512,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T02:52:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181002/20512743\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181002%2F20512743&d=bkMff%2BmN1HGnJVfal0EyEfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=3c85367f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181002%2F20512743&h=77bea7cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181002/20512743</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月02日 <br />\n<br />\n傘運紀錄片　入圍金馬獎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181002/large/a0504a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181002%2Flarge%2Fa0504a.gif&h=504f9c03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《傘上：遍地開花》部份版權屬電視台，未能在院線放映。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】台灣第55屆金馬獎昨日在台北公佈入圍名單，今屆無論是最佳男、女主角、最佳導演，都沒有香港電影人入圍，只得惠英紅和袁富華同樣憑電影《翠絲》入圍男、女配角獎項；最佳電影方面，亦沒有香港電影入圍，但以雨傘運動為題材的港產片《傘上：遍地開花》入圍角逐最佳紀錄片，對手還有《四個春天》、《後勁：王建民》、《我們的青春，在台灣》和《24號大街》。<br />\n<br />\n香港的《傘上：遍地開花》與台灣的《我們的青春，在台灣》同時入圍最佳紀錄片，兩片分別記錄港台追求民主的社會運動，別具時代意義。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n導演為移居星洲港人<br />\n<br />\n《傘上：遍地開花》由梁思眾執導，梁思眾是70年代新浪潮導演梁普智之子，他生於香港，10歲已移民，現在是新加坡公民。<br />\n<br />\n梁思眾經常替外國的廣播公司拍攝紀錄片，賺取開拍電影的資金。《傘上：遍地開花》片長119分鐘，而且只是上集。由於《傘上：遍地開花》部份片段的版權屬於電視台，因此影片雖然可以公開放映，但不能營利，所以無法在院線上放映。<br />\n<br />\n2014年爆發的雨傘運動，是爭取真普選的公民抗命運動。示威者及學生自發佔據多個主要馬路進行靜坐及遊行，佔領區包括金鐘、添馬艦、中環、灣仔、銅鑼灣、旺角及尖沙嘴，由金鐘開始遍地開花，示威者撐傘對抗清場警員。<br />\n<br />\n■記者王麗春  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n女記者摑人　央視反促保守黨道歉<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n泛民新召集人　毛孟靜講數唔拍枱"},{"pid":"9555a2ecd6269ea180781feb87165ee298125ace","tid":844512,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T02:54:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18cb1d6456f7132cf0b46235f5cc8299d3f7212","tid":844512,"uid":51720,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T03:01:04.000Z","msg":"猜測：當局或會聯同電視台，以版權為由禁映(包括義映在內) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8175b3dd79502e001df5545721542c07c162b9e4","tid":844512,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T03:10:22.000Z","msg":"地厚天高呢？"},{"pid":"921aeef54a59e36990a9a4d4a845fadb8ab58022","tid":844512,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8175b3dd79502e001df5545721542c07c162b9e4","tid":844512,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T03:10:22.000Z","msg":"地厚天高呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T03:11:02.000Z","msg":"我都以為係呢套入圍。"},{"pid":"8a7f66ed557bd6367f36633d84b271980a71ab76","tid":844512,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T03:32:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a732b161071f99efffa093e098d9dcb66e4a71","tid":844512,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T03:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93346daae3d6dc8e0e61aca8e0bf2e8a870e595","tid":844512,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:06:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d842d19260af68e36f07468e318792e0d261630","tid":844512,"uid":98032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"921aeef54a59e36990a9a4d4a845fadb8ab58022","tid":844512,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8175b3dd79502e001df5545721542c07c162b9e4","tid":8